<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女人从一栋高档的SPA会所走出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她伸手从包里拿出一面小镜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！”她说，“那个SPA太神奇了，我看上去......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，她开始发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她变得越来越小了。然后……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咕…咕！嘎…嘎！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢艾普卡特老师给我们自由时间。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在画一艘宇宙飞船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉从书中抬起头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是高兴快放学了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我跟你们说了我的好消息了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔扬起一边的眉毛。“什么消息？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟我们说说！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有工作了。”玛拉说，“从今天放学后开始！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”杰克大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾普卡特老师抬起头。“嘘！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转过头看着玛拉小声说，“哇！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么工作？”特勒尔问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会在商店里工作吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克咧嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会经营一家大公司，赚很多很多钱吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要去做老板吗？”特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和特勒尔笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去给一个妈妈做帮手！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真了不起！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是去照看小孩子，对吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！我去帮邻居加森太太。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她要办一个派对，需要我照看她两岁的孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，加森太太也会在那儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跟照看小孩子不完全一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也想工作。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我不喜欢照看小孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想经营大公司，赚很多很多钱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“照看小孩子是件很难的事情。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我相信火箭女孩儿一定做得很好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉又转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西也转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿有更重要的事情要做，特勒尔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她问艾普卡特老师能不能去一下洗手间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她走到走廊上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么…哇！您变得好年轻啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长的脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，谢谢! 今天早上我去SPA会所做了一个特殊护理。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我感觉非常好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那有什么问题吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长愣了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，对了！我们遇到一个很奇怪的问题，火箭女孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城管道供应公司的老板，库珀先生不见了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这还不算，他的办公室出现一个婴儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西挠了挠头。“是很奇怪哦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过您不用担心，市长先生！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我马上就去看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>